00:02:43.380 --> 00:02:45.600
That's what the name Jehovah means.

00:02:45.600 --> 00:02:50.380
The root word, the Hebrew root word for Jehovah is hayah,

00:02:50.380 --> 00:02:55.380
and that literally means to be, to be.

00:02:55.539 --> 00:02:57.419
Now, pause just for a moment

00:02:57.419 --> 00:02:59.660
