00:03:09.020 --> 00:03:13.979
into conversation, and you say, in the beginning, God.

00:03:13.979 --> 00:03:15.580
Well, who created God?

00:03:15.580 --> 00:03:18.779
No one created God, and the wonderful truth

00:03:18.779 --> 00:03:21.580
that God gave to us in revealing to us

00:03:22.020 --> 00:03:26.300
this great dynamic truth is that his name Jehovah

00:03:26.300 --> 00:03:28.940
