00:03:55.179 --> 00:03:58.740
the difference between Jehovah and Adonai.

00:03:58.740 --> 00:04:03.139
Adonai would be a capital L with a little O-R-D,

00:04:03.139 --> 00:04:06.380
and it makes the distinction between the two names of God,

00:04:06.380 --> 00:04:08.259
Jehovah and Adonai.

00:04:08.259 --> 00:04:10.580
