00:04:18.820 --> 00:04:20.380
We're gonna study a lot of them,

00:04:20.459 --> 00:04:22.339
and we found, even as we looked last week,

00:04:22.339 --> 00:04:26.700
Jehovah-Jireh, that compound name of our God.

00:04:26.700 --> 00:04:28.220
We're here in Exodus chapter number three.

