00:09:57.940 --> 00:09:59.140
Notice this phrase,

00:09:59.140 --> 00:10:00.020
and I.

00:10:00.020 --> 00:10:05.760
I will redeem you with a stretched-out arm

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:07.800
